{"tid":1713400,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［罷工罷課文宣方向］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷","createTime":"2019-11-12T17:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T03:39:41.000Z","uid":312125,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"da6f90011b432e1b5c4405b9844d0a77afad3122","tid":1713400,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係香港春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動，叫無知市民學生盡快參與三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">今日黑警突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">尋日中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">今日警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警告⚠️堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬🦖強姦殺人滅口💀嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請文宣盡快製圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>旺角恐襲</strong><br />\n旺角月台怪怪地<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1710512\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1710512</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中環TG</strong><br />\n中環TG放題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1710806\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1710806</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>挑釁學生</strong><br />\n亂捉學生妹<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/258224170919874/posts/2609575109118090?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F258224170919874%2Fposts%2F2609575109118090%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=dc746623\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/258224170919874/posts/2609575109118090?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好多popo圍住葵涌邨既中華基督教會全完中學<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1710866\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1710866</a><br />\n<br />\